    <h2> Today - The spicy soup </h2>
    <p> In the school canteen was served a soup to a student in 11-th grade. He claims that this soup was an ordinary pepper soup served by the school. But there was a twist!It was hotter than the pepper used to make it! </p>
    <p> The student said that he felt like his mouth was on fire and that he had to drink a lot of water to cool it down. He also said that the soup was so spicy that it made him sweat and cry. </p>
    <p> The school administration has not yet commented on the incident, but they have promised to investigate the matter and take appropriate action if necessary. </p>
